because of Max leaving.

25:18.440 --> 25:20.591
Depressed?
No, I could've managed that.

25:20.800 --> 25:23.474
No, I'm...
Julie's always been a moody kid.

25:23.680 --> 25:25.990
I wouldn't have even bothered
to call you.

25:26.200 --> 25:27.236
Well, why not?

25:27.440 --> 25:30.080
Because, Linda,
you don't really give a damn.

25:30.280 --> 25:31.634
Yes, I do!

25:33.960 --> 25:36.395
